Title: Designates the tugboat Urger as the official tugboat of the state of New York
Summary: Designates the tugboat Urger as the official tugboat of the state of New York.
ActClause: AN ACT an act to amend the state law, in relation to designating the tugboat Urger as the official tugboat of the state of New York
